How to watch a course to learn this?
First watch
No practice
A quick pass
Knowing what all is in the course
Becoming aware
Getting interested
Take notes to make the second pass useful. What is important? What achieves what?
Second watch
Practice with watching
Build confidence
No cramming still
Not learning to impress but learning to build a reference index for building phase
Third watch
Review and think where I lack confidence
Rewatch and practice selectively
